{"TopicId":91463,"ForumId":38,"TopicTitle":"Bad Suggestions for KSP","CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T12:38:29Z","PageNum":6,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T14:10:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll engines should have 3.75m tank butts, no one makes small rockets anymore.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"icedown","CreatedById":129659,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T14:19:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRandom events like staging, activating actions with increasing probability as stupidity factor of crew, as noted by the highest value, increases.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T17:02:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReplace Kerbals with 3D models of Elmo from Sesame street.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Andem","CreatedById":155578,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T19:37:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222785282\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475504387\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129659\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022icedown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, icedown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRandom events like staging, activating actions with increasing probability as stupidity factor of crew, as noted by the highest value, increases.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlright, again, if done well this could be kind of fun. Give a reason to balance out crews maybe.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RocketSquid","CreatedById":152665,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T21:45:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe inevitable problem that arises when adding life support is that even if you take it directly from a very well-liked mod, users of other mods will have objections. The solution is simple: Add all of them. All at once.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOf course you\u0027d need to be able to turn life support off, so that it doesn\u0027t break established saves or make the game too daunting for new players, but it would of course be all-or-nothing since we don\u0027t need that many options clogging up our difficulty menu.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T23:09:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it\u0027s time to change the theme of the game. Instead of building rockets, we can create ladders and catwalks\u00A0to go everywhere.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"limeyptwo","CreatedById":165572,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T23:54:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222781918\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475277647\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155697\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ackoli\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/30/2016 at 4:20 PM, Ackoli said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMICROTRANSACTIONS! GUNZ! NUKS! ALEINS! BLUD! VIOLDENCE! RAINBOWZ EVERYHWERE! MORE BLUD! MORE VIOLDENCE! TURN IT INTO A COPY OF GTA BUT WITH KERBALZ! \u00A0EVILNESS! EA! MORE STUF! STAR WARS SPACECRAFT! AND MORE EPICNARS!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222778408\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475093071\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022142607\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022legoclone09\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/28/2016 at 1:04 PM, legoclone09 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow about Grand Theft Rover?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-04T01:53:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222781918\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475277647\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155697\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ackoli\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 30/09/2016 at 7:20 PM, Ackoli said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMICROTRANSACTIONS! GUNZ! NUKS! ALEINS! BLUD! VIOLDENCE! RAINBOWZ EVERYHWERE! MORE BLUD! MORE VIOLDENCE! TURN IT INTO A COPY OF GTA BUT WITH KERBALZ! \u00A0EVILNESS! EA! MORE STUF! STAR WARS SPACECRAFT! AND MORE EPICNARS!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!DAIRECTD BY MIKEL BAY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-04T05:16:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222786031\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475536142\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135127\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Matuchkin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Matuchkin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it\u0027s time to change the theme of the game. Instead of building rockets, we can create ladders and catwalks\u00A0to go everywhere.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVery nice idea. I additionally suggest transcontinental pipelines.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222785282\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475504387\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129659\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022icedown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, icedown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRandom events like staging, activating actions with increasing probability as stupidity factor of crew, as noted by the highest value, increases.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, DangIt and Kerbalism mods do kind of that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222786091\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475538894\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165572\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022limeyptwo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, limeyptwo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow about Grand Theft Rover?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWithout citizens? What\u0027s fun?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"insert_name","CreatedById":150339,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-04T07:15:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EADD MOAR DRES!!!!!!!!!!!!\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"55delta","CreatedById":101735,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-04T09:58:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSimulate N-body physics through code similar to the following: when game_time = (1 hour),\u00A0prograde_vector =\u00A0prograde_vector \u002B rand(0-359) degrees\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chabadarl","CreatedById":169589,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-04T10:09:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSuppress timewarp\u00A0and add a\u00A0KCT-style feature. Building a rocket takes a month IRL. You cannot\u00A0recover to launch or \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E anymore.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0 \u00A0 \u00A0 \u00A0 \u00A0...Yep! you forget to put a solar panel on this probe see you next month...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-04T10:26:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222786615\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475575796\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022169589\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Chabadarl\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, Chabadarl said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSuppress timewarp\u00A0and add a\u00A0KCT-style feature. Building a rocket takes a month IRL. You cannot\u00A0recover to launch or \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E anymore.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0 \u00A0 \u00A0 \u00A0 \u00A0...Yep! you forget to put a solar panel on this probe see you next month...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cs\u003EAnd suffocate IRL if cannot return a craft from orbit.\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake KSP online multiplayer, with player\u0027s account attached to his/her real Visa/Mastercard, and penalize IRL for lost rockets.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"icedown","CreatedById":129659,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-05T01:49:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222786434\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475558188\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, DangIt and Kerbalism mods do kind of that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, nothing as nice as them. I don\u0027t think Jeb is quite that friendly with parts\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Firemetal","CreatedById":164725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T03:11:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake Dres the only planet in the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T05:11:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake Dres The Only Planet a gas giant.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"insert_name","CreatedById":150339,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T05:27:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKidnap the recently former devs and glue them to their desk chairs\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T08:48:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIncrease Kerbin radius \u002B1%.\u003Cbr\u003E\n(Hi, all nav and scenery mods...)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMove landscape 1 km in random directions.\u003Cbr\u003E\n(...especially Kerbin-Side)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd (as suggested earlier), increase the sitting Kerbal model \u002B10% in size.\u003Cbr\u003E\n(Or more, if they still match the command pods interiors).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T21:10:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222786622\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475576779\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 04/10/2016 at 6:26 AM, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cs\u003EAnd suffocate IRL if cannot return a craft from orbit.\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake KSP online multiplayer, with player\u0027s account attached to his/her real Visa/Mastercard, and penalize IRL for lost rockets.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith Realism Overhaul, the costs for each rocket will be equivalent of rocket parts used in real life.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T22:28:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn order to make a rocket in-game, you have to pay someone to build and fly it IRL.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"55delta","CreatedById":101735,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-07T01:00:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nImplement Real Solar System in stock, but leave stock parts unadjusted.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-08T22:35:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222778375\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475091702\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022163034\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheKosanianMethod\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/28/2016 at 0:41 PM, TheKosanianMethod said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want weather implemented. High winds, muddy dirt is hard to land on, the runway becomes slick when it rains.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd have launch delays due to\u00A0bad weather conditions, requiring rollbacks. Extreme weather would require restarting KSP, or even rebooting the PC. If on console, thunderstorms would corrupt the save!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-12T13:10:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRemove Dres.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RocketSquid","CreatedById":152665,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-15T13:03:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo compromise between adding more Dres and removing Dres, give Dres a larger radius but make it hemispherical.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HansonKerman","CreatedById":185809,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-09T14:50:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003Ea\u00A0\u201Cnecromancy\u201D button. When pressed by an EVAing Kerbal or accessed from the toolbar, it revives all terminated missions (and replaces their name with \u201CNECROMANCY!!\u201D)\u00A0, all dead or \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Missing in action\u0022\u003EMIA\u003C/abbr\u003E Kerbals\u00A0(albeit named \u201CMERASMUS!\u201D), all crafts you have ever deleted, named UNDEAD!!!! and all forum threads with the post \u201CNECROMANCY!!\u00A1\u201D by the person \u003Cspan\u003E@\u003C/span\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ENecromancer.\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00221551613\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221417180052\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227187\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Felsmak\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/28/2014 at 8:07 AM, Felsmak said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHats for Kerbals. Lots of them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003Ethis is a necromancy quote\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003Eand that would be bad how?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}